item.title: CVE-2017-5695|2024-08-05T15:11:48.446Z -- intel%20corporation -- solid-state%20drive%20consumer%2C%20professional%2C%20embedded%2C%20data%20center
item.description: Data corruption vulnerability in firmware in Intel Solid-State Drive Consumer, Professional, Embedded, Data Center affected firmware versions LSBG200, LSF031C, LSF036C, LBF010C, LSBG100, LSF031C, LSF036C, LBF010C, LSF031P, LSF036P, LBF010P, LSF031P, LSF036P, LBF010P, LSMG200, LSF031E, LSF036E, LSMG100, LSF031E, LSF036E, LSDG200, LSF031D, LSF036D allows local users to cause a denial of service via unspecified vectors.
